{
  "texts": [
    "These platforms offer advanced features tailored specifically for creating, editing, and managing human-or machinegenerated ADs, thus providing significant advantages over more general-purpose tools.",
    "Machine-generated ADs often contain grammatical errors and other undesirable elements.",
    "To address this issue, text editing models are developed and trained to improve the quality of these texts.",
    "These models typically utilize training data that includes human-simplified or corrected texts (Faltings et al., 2021; Kim et al., 2022; Zhang et al., 2023b).",
    "Among these, many LLMbased models are fine-tuned with instructions (Raheja et al., 2023 (Raheja et al.,, 2024;; Shu et al., 2024; Ki and Carpuat, 2024), while others are trained using semi-autoregressive or non-autoregressive decoding techniques (Mallinson et al., 2022; Agrawal and Carpuat, 2022; Zhang et al., 2023b)."
  ]
}